{"tid":1177270,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"菅田将暉 2nd Album「LOVE」集中討論區 (1)","createTime":"2019-05-29T16:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T17:35:41.000Z","uid":1262,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb1524c0c5339f340fdfbd8992d1120e3d95e2c","tid":1177270,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"2nd Album「LOVE」<br />\n2019.07.10 Release<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/05/30/t9GuPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F05%2F30%2Ft9GuPB.jpg&h=8e473f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLOVE<br />\n2019年7月10日（三）發行<br />\n <br />\n完全生産限定盤<br />\n【内容物】CD＋圖相冊（收錄64頁專輯製作的相關圖像）<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/05/30/waOX9J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F05%2F30%2FwaOX9J.png&h=5722325d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菅田將暉LIVE TOUR 2019&ldquo;LOVE&rdquo;<br />\n8月24日（六）福岡Zepp Fukuoka<br />\n8月29日（四）愛知Zepp Nagoya<br />\n8月31日（六）大阪Zepp Osaka Bayside<br />\n9月5日（四）東京Zepp DiverCity TOKYO<br />\n9月6日（五）東京Zepp DiverCity TOKYO"},{"pid":"46d37b1ae1fe599c5e6d0911e4c40023aa37a6ea","tid":1177270,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"新歌まちがいさがし連續兩星期佔日本billboard首位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d739c0e3687e324d219ed9e0e1d023c2464a645e","tid":1177270,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T17:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/05/30/47uOqH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F05%2F30%2F47uOqH.png&h=acfb1fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/05/30/zJ2r1w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F05%2F30%2FzJ2r1w.png&h=b174458c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https:/